            and connect with others. Whether itâ€™s a story, an experience, 
            or some wisdom youâ€™d like to pass along, this space is for you.<br>
            <br>Letâ€™s build a community of shared knowledge, ideas, and support!</p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Footer -->

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Cozy Blog | Created by Vasiliki Loli</p>
    </footer>


</body>
</html>
